  "question": "<p>(1) Did the Circuit Court use the proper standard of evidence for establishing that an employer's asserted nondiscriminatory reason for a hiring decision is pretextual? (2) Can an employer's use of the word \"boy\" to refer to an employee ever be evidence of racial animus?</p>\n",
